[[恰克·貝瑞|恰克·貝瑞]]於1980年代後期首次將其「{{le|未經授權傳記|Unauthorized biography|未經授權自傳}}」《危險心靈的自白》（{{lang|en|''Confessions of a Dangerous Mind''}}）的{{le|電影版權|Film rights}}賣給[[哥倫比亞影業|哥倫比亞影業]]。哥倫比亞總裁{{le|黛恩·史蒂爾|Dawn Steel}}選來{{le|吉姆·麥克布萊德|Jim McBride}}擔任導演後[[綠燈_(電影製作)|批准]]製作改編電影《神經殺手》。<ref name="Variety(1997-06-05)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1997/voices/columns/60s-revivals-spur-rivals-1116679932/|title=’60s revivals spur rivals|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=1997-06-05|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923103638/https://variety.com/1997/voices/columns/60s-revivals-spur-rivals-1116679932/|archive-date=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>麥克布萊德找來[[李察·德雷福斯|李察·德雷福斯]]擔任主角，後者因厭惡貝瑞的[[黑色幽默|病態幽默]]而拒絕閱讀劇本<ref name="NYTimes(2002-12-22)">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/12/22/movies/film-man-with-a-mission-get-the-film-made.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|title=FILM; Man With a Mission: Get the Film Made|last=Thompson|first=Anne|work=The New York Times|date=2002-12-22|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928070809/https://www.nytimes.com/2002/12/22/movies/film-man-with-a-mission-get-the-film-made.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|archive-date=2013-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該項目於1989年史蒂爾離開公司時被放棄<ref name="Variety(1997-06-05)" />。製片人{{le|安德魯·拉薩|Andrew Lazar}}於1997年從哥倫比亞手中買下版權，同年交由[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]公司發展。[[查理·考夫曼|查理·考夫曼]]於1997年6月開始受雇編寫新的劇本，<ref name="Variety(1997-06-05)" />並於當年下半年完成初稿。貝瑞本人對考夫曼的劇本給予好評<ref name="BehindTheScenes">{{cite AV media|people=Clooney, George; Barris, Chuck; Rockwell, Sam|date=2003|title=Behind The Scenes of Confessions of a Dangerous Mind|medium=Behind The Scenes|publisher=[[華特迪士尼家庭娛樂公司|Miramax Home Entertainment]]}}</ref>，[[柯提斯·韓森|柯提斯·韓森]]立即同意執導並由[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]主演<ref name="BBCOnline(2003-03-04)">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/03/04/george_clooney_confessions_of_a_dangerous_mind_interview.shtml|title=George Clooney: Confessions of a Dangerous Mind|last=Pierce|first=Nev|work=[[BBC在線|BBC Online]]|date=2003-03-04|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117024120/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2003/03/04/george_clooney_confessions_of_a_dangerous_mind_interview.shtml|archive-date=2020-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[喬治·克隆尼|喬治·克隆尼]]和[[茱兒·芭莉摩|茱兒·芭莉摩]]被聘來加入演出陣容<ref name="Variety(2000-12-10)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2000/film/news/dangerous-dealings-1117790270/|title=‘Dangerous’ dealings|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=Variety|date=2000-12-10|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306202423/https://variety.com/2000/film/news/dangerous-dealings-1117790270/|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="About.com-1">{{cite news|url=http://movies.about.com/library/weekly/aaconfessionsinta.htm|title=George Clooney Talks About "Confessions of a Dangerous Mind"|last1=Murray|first1=Rebecca|last2=Topel|first2=Fred|work=[[Dotdash|About.com]]|accessdate=2021-01-31|page=1|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060214164109/http://movies.about.com/library/weekly/aaconfessionsinta.htm|archive-date=2006-02-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="About.com-2">{{cite news|url=http://movies.about.com/library/weekly/aaconfessionsintc.htm|title=George Clooney Talks About "Confessions of a Dangerous Mind"|last1=Murray|first1=Rebecca|last2=Topel|first2=Fred|work=About.com|accessdate=2021-01-31|page=2|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204175349/http://movies.about.com/library/weekly/aaconfessionsintc.htm|archive-date=2009-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

韓森最終退出；在《[[新娘不是我|新娘不是我]]》（1997年）賣座後，{{le|P·J·賀根|P. J. Hogan}}於1998年1月開始與華納兄弟會談，以執導《神經殺手》。<ref name="Variety(1998-01-06)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1998/film/news/hogan-game-for-barris-bio-1117434320/|title=Hogan game for Barris bio|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=Variety|date=1998-01-06|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503081833/https://variety.com/1998/film/news/hogan-game-for-barris-bio-1117434320/|archive-date=2016-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>西恩·潘辭去主演後，[[麥克·邁爾斯|麥克·邁爾斯]]簽約接替<ref name="Variety(1998-08-10)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1998/film/news/myers-wb-will-doo-two-1117479305/|title=Myers, WB will ‘Doo’ two|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=Variety|date=1998-08-10|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923082736/https://variety.com/1998/film/news/myers-wb-will-doo-two-1117479305/|archive-date=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，華納兄弟與賀根的會談破裂。[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]、[[大衛·芬奇|大衛·芬奇]]和[[戴倫·艾洛諾夫斯基|戴倫·艾洛諾夫斯基]]都對接任導演一職感興趣。<ref name="NYTimes(2002-12-22)" /><ref name="Variety(2000-03-21)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2000/digital/news/inside-moves-164-1117779742/|title=Inside Moves|author=Staff|work=Variety|date=2000-03-21|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014114630/https://variety.com/2000/digital/news/inside-moves-164-1117779742/|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="EW(1997-07-30)">{{cite news|url=https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,272563,00.html|title=Best Unproduced Screenplays|last=Shaw|first=Jessica|work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=1997-07-30|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623100833/https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,272563,00.html|archive-date=2011-06-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>芬奇和曼德斯於2000年4月積極競爭加入《神經殺手》的製作<ref name="Variety(2000-04-11)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2000/voices/columns/george-hamilton-s-mom-may-be-subject-of-pic-1117780417/|title=George Hamilton’s mom may be subject of pic|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=Variety|date=2000-04-11|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306075532/https://variety.com/2000/voices/columns/george-hamilton-s-mom-may-be-subject-of-pic-1117780417/|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，芬奇最終率先退出。同年10月，成為共同出資方的{{le|文藝復興製片公司|Renaissance Pictures}}找來[[布萊恩·狄帕瑪|布萊恩·狄帕瑪]]執導電影<ref name="Variety(2000-10-20)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2000/film/news/renaissance-slates-two-1117788063/|title=Renaissance slates two|last=Dawtrey|first=Adam|work=Variety|date=2000-10-20|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923102549/https://variety.com/2000/film/news/renaissance-slates-two-1117788063/|archive-date=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本月晚些，華納兄弟將該項目{{le|周轉 (電影製作)|Turnaround (filmmaking)|周轉}}<ref name="Variety(2000-10-23)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2000/film/news/ieg-mighty-in-blighty-1117788148/|title=IEG mighty in Blighty|last1=Lyons|first1=Charles|last2=Hopewell|first2=John|work=Variety|date=2000-10-23|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628011509/https://variety.com/2000/film/news/ieg-mighty-in-blighty-1117788148/|archive-date=2017-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且曼德斯已失去興趣<ref name="Variety(2000-12-10)" />。演員[[羅素·克洛|羅素·克洛]]、[[凱文·史貝西|凱文·史貝西]]和[[艾德華·諾頓|艾德華·諾頓]]在電影早期的發展階段也都對該片深感興趣<ref name="EW(2003-01-10)">{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,403596,00.html|title=The Gong Goodbye|last=Valby|first=Karen|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2003-01-10|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100528121340/https://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,403596,00.html|archive-date=2010-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2000年12月，[[班·史提勒|班·史提勒]]有望飾演恰克·貝瑞，[[布萊恩·辛格|布萊恩·辛格]]成為導演人選，克隆尼仍在演出陣容中。然而，由於與《[[名模大間諜|名模大間諜]]》和《[[天才一族|天才一族]]》（均為2001年）的拍攝日程發生衝突，史提勒被迫放棄《神經殺手》<ref name="Variety(2000-12-10)" />。雖然辛格有興趣讓[[山姆·洛克威爾|山姆·洛克威爾]]擔任主演<ref name="NYTimes(2003-01-03)">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/01/03/movies/at-the-movies.html?n=Top%2fFeatures%2fMovies%2fColumns%2fAt%20the%20Movies|title=At The Movies|last=Kehr|first=Dave|work=The New York Times|date=2003-01-03|accessdate=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129140956/https://www.nytimes.com/2003/01/03/movies/at-the-movies.html?n=Top%2fFeatures%2fMovies%2fColumns%2fAt%20the%20Movies|archive-date=2018-01-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他仍選了[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]來接替史提勒，並計劃2001年1月以3500萬美元的預算<ref name="Variety(2001-03-26)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/more/news/renaissance-axes-sales-chiefs-1117797832/|title=Renaissance axes sales chiefs|last=Dawtrey|first=Adam|work=Variety|date=2001-03-26|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923095637/https://variety.com/2001/more/news/renaissance-axes-sales-chiefs-1117797832/|archive-date=2020-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>展開{{le|前期製作|Pre-production}}<ref name="Variety(2001-01-09)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/film/news/depp-clooney-game-for-barris-biopic-1117791592/|title=Depp, Clooney game for Barris biopic|last=Harris|first=Dana|work=Variety|date=2001-01-09|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129192050/https://variety.com/2001/film/news/depp-clooney-game-for-barris-biopic-1117791592/|archive-date=2017-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。文藝復興製片公司持有國際發行權，但電影製作方仍需要更多的資金，再加上一家片商來負責美國的發行工作<ref name="Variety(2001-01-09)" />。

{{le|格羅夫納公園製片公司|Grosvenor Park Productions}}有興趣與文藝復興共同出資<ref name="Variety(2001-01-30)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/film/news/grosvenor-fund-eyes-teuton-tie-1117792937/|title=Grosvenor fund eyes Teuton tie|last=Dawtrey|first=Adam|work=Variety|date=2001-01-30|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014114857/https://variety.com/2001/film/news/grosvenor-fund-eyes-teuton-tie-1117792937/|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但下個月（2001年2月），《神經殺手》再次停滯不前。[[米拉麥克斯影業|米拉麥克斯影業]]不斷地想取得北美發行權，但當也想涵蓋國際發行權時碰壁。文藝復興也無法及時完成融資，以趕上「製作保險」的最後期限和65天的{{le|拍攝時程表|Shooting schedule}}<ref name="Variety(2001-02-15)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/film/news/mind-games-stall-1117793836/|title=‘Mind’ games stall|last1=Dunkley|first1=Cathy|last2=Harris|first2=Dana|work=Variety|date=2001-02-15|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014114921/https://variety.com/2001/film/news/mind-games-stall-1117793836/|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>；[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]地點定在加拿大[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]和[[英屬哥倫比亞省|英屬哥倫比亞省]]<ref name="Variety(2001-03-06)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/film/news/sound-shoot-off-as-strike-threat-looms-1117794870/|title=‘Sound’ shoot off as strike threat looms|last=Kelly|first=Brendan|work=Variety|date=2001-03-06|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610035542/https://variety.com/2001/film/news/sound-shoot-off-as-strike-threat-looms-1117794870/|archive-date=2019-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Variety(2001-02-25)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/biz/news/canuck-prod-n-rises-1117794232/|title=Canuck prod’n rises|last1=Townson|first1=Don|last2=Kelly|first2=Brendan|work=Variety|date=2001-02-25|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014114931/https://variety.com/2001/biz/news/canuck-prod-n-rises-1117794232/|archive-date=2016-10-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|工匠娛樂|Artisan Entertainment}}也對北美發行權感興趣，但在出價超過800萬美元後退出。強尼·戴普最後退出改拍其他電影。<ref name="Variety(2001-02-15)" />

=== 導演和劇本 ===
辛格正忙於準備《[[X戰警2|X戰警2]]》時，克隆尼接任了《神經殺手》導演一職，這也是他的導演處女作<ref name="Variety(2001-01-25)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2001/film/columns/dish-er-doc-cuts-big-deal-1117801914/|title=Dish: ‘ER’ doc cuts big deal|last=Fleming|first=Michael|work=Variety|date=2001-01-25|accessdate=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910065029/https://variety.com/2001/film/columns/dish-er-doc-cuts-big-deal-1117801914/|archive-date=2019-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CinemaBlend(2019-05-28)" />。米拉麥克斯影業同意承擔發行職責並共同資助該片。《神經殺手》的資金來自米拉麥克斯、克隆尼自己的{{le|第八節製片公司|Section Eight Productions}}、[[威秀電影|威秀電影]]、安德魯·拉薩的瘋狂機會（{{lang|en|Mad Chance}}）、{{le|聯合電影公司|Allied Filmmakers}}及{{le|庫許納-洛克公司|The Kushner-Locke Company}}。<ref name="Variety(2001-01-25)" />克隆尼表示：「我想如果我擔任導演的工作是為了掌控權，且能夠便宜地聘請其他所有人，如果我能把這部電影的價格降低到3000萬美元，那我將能夠製作這部電影。這是我向米拉麥克斯的[[哈維·溫斯坦|哈維·溫斯坦]]推銷的重要部分。」<ref name="About.com-1" />

